    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, and the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs quietly and powerfully, and every feature and component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for and kept in climate-controlled storage.",
      "price": 48500.0,
